In determining the order of priority of a certified activity recommended for funding, the Minister shall consider the following:
* the efficiency of implementation of the certified activity;
* the impact of the certified activity on the community and the environment;
* the impact of the certified activity on the implementation of the National Environment Policy; and
* the relative merits of continuing funding for the community group or organisation in receipt of funding as against funding the certified activities of new groups and organisations.
